node.text:
heLLO it's finally here!! 💜 my new klance zine is now up for preorder at my store => ikimaru.bigcartel.com (link in bio) 💜

preorders will stay open until aug 5! (maybe a bit longer but that’s the main date)

bunch of things happened and I had to push this back for months so, I'm really glad it's finally wrapped up ahah 😩👌

anyway, 46 pages of fluff, kissing, cuddling, some aus, some in canon and post canon stuff, I compiled all my fav illustration I made since 2019 until now and includes a bunch of pictures that aren't currently posted online! (16 as of now)

⭐ more info in the product listing in the store!

⭐ once preorders are done, production time will be at least 2 more weeks, hopefully I can send out everything within august but I'll keep you updated!

⭐ if you get the PDF along with the printed copy, you can get to see all those pics asap without having have to wait until then c:

⭐ if you also order one of my previous zines along with it, you can get a 4€ discount with code ZINEBUNDLE (doesn’t apply to PDF-only versions of zines)

thank you for reading and for sticking around, it's amazing I still get to share these characters with you in 2021! ❤️💙

if you have questions let me know ✨

#klance #keithkogane #lancemcclain #zine #bigcartel
